<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Ancient:SoS</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
285 - (15%SMC 10%Spec 15%Earring) = 171mana<br>
1150 + (15%Focus 7%SCF) = 1403dmg<br>
<br>
1403 / 171 = 8.2 dmg / mana<br>
<br>
PetDPS + NukeDPS = TargetDPS<br>
<br>
NukeDPS = 8.2 * ManaRegen/6<br>
<br>
8.2 * ManaRegen/6 = TargetDPS - PetDPS<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>ManaRegen = (TargetDPS - PetDPS) * (6 / 8.2)</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
If TargetDPS = 200, PetDPS = 80 then <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Manaregen = 87</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Possible sources of Mana regen?<br>
<br>
Tranq:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 16<br>
Horse:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 22<br>
Bard:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 21<br>
Druid:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 8<br>
FT:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 15<br>
MC:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 3<br>
Natural:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 1<br>
SD:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 9<br>
Rods:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 4<br>
Water Form:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 2<br>
<br>
Total:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 101<br>
<br>
It's <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>possible</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->. I'm not saying it's easily achiveable, but possible <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
